OL,5, Prime Minister Boris Johnson has       
OL,6, unveiled plans to allow benefits to be 
OL,7, put towards mortgages in England, as he
OL,8, sought to relaunch his premiership.    
OL,10,FHe made the "benefits-to-bricks" pledge
OL,11,Fin his first big speech since surviving
OL,12,Fa bid to oust him by Tory MPs.         
OL,14,FSpeaking in Blackpool, he also vowed to
OL,15,Fextend a scheme to allow social tenants
OL,16,Fto buy their homes.                    
OL,18,FBut critics say the proposals are      
OL,19,Funworkable and would make the housing  
OL,20,Fcrisis worse.                          
